        <div class="bw-flow__decision-grid" aria-label="Wardrobe finish direction references">
          <article class="bw-flow__decision-card">
            <span class="bw-flow__decision-media"><img src="{{ wardrobe_preview_primary_src }}" alt="{{ wardrobe_preview_primary_alt }}" loading="lazy" width="720" height="540"></span>
            <strong>Warm practical storage</strong>
            <p>Engineered wood, laminate shutters, and a calmer finish direction suit bedrooms where daily use matters more than visual drama.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="bw-flow__decision-card">
            <span class="bw-flow__decision-media"><img src="{{ wardrobe_preview_secondary_src }}" alt="{{ wardrobe_preview_secondary_alt }}" loading="lazy" width="720" height="540"></span>
            <strong>Balanced premium</strong>
