          <article class="bw-flow__decision-card">
            <span class="bw-flow__decision-media"><img src="{{ wardrobe_preview_tertiary_src }}" alt="{{ wardrobe_preview_tertiary_alt }}" loading="lazy" width="720" height="540"></span>
            <strong>Mirror-led statement</strong>
            <p>Glass, mirror, and profile-led fronts make more sense when the wardrobe also needs to lift the room visually.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
        <div class="bw-flow__section">
          <div class="bw-flow__label">Carcass material</div>
          <div class="bw-flow__choices" data-flow-group="carcass">
            <label class="bw-flow__choice bw-flow__choice--image is-selected"><input type="radio" name="wardrobe_carcass" value="Engineered wood" checked>
              <span class="bw-flow__choice-media"><img src="{{ wardrobe_preview_primary_src }}" alt="{{ wardrobe_preview_primary_alt }}" loading="lazy" width="720" height="540"></span>
              <span class="bw-flow__choice-copy"><span class="bw-flow__choice-title">Engineered Wood</span><span class="bw-flow__choice-note">A balanced practical base for value-led briefs and everyday use.</span></span>
            </label>
            <label class="bw-flow__choice bw-flow__choice--image"><input type="radio" name="wardrobe_carcass" value="Plywood">
              <span class="bw-flow__choice-media"><img src="{{ wardrobe_preview_secondary_src }}" alt="{{ wardrobe_preview_secondary_alt }}" loading="lazy" width="720" height="540"></span>
              <span class="bw-flow__choice-copy"><span class="bw-flow__choice-title">Plywood</span><span class="bw-flow__choice-note">A stronger structural direction for customers who want a more durable cabinet feel.</span></span>
            </label>
            <label class="bw-flow__choice bw-flow__choice--image"><input type="radio" name="wardrobe_carcass" value="Need guidance">
              <span class="bw-flow__choice-media"><img src="{{ wardrobe_preview_tertiary_src }}" alt="{{ wardrobe_preview_tertiary_alt }}" loading="lazy" width="720" height="540"></span>
              <span class="bw-flow__choice-copy"><span class="bw-flow__choice-title">Need Guidance</span><span class="bw-flow__choice-note">Use this when you want Bluewud to guide the material decision with the brief.</span></span>
            </label>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="bw-flow__section">
          <div class="bw-flow__label">Shutter material</div>
          <div class="bw-flow__choices" data-flow-group="shutter_material">
            <label class="bw-flow__choice bw-flow__choice--image is-selected"><input type="radio" name="wardrobe_shutter_material" value="Laminate panel" checked>
              <span class="bw-flow__choice-media"><img src="{{ wardrobe_preview_primary_src }}" alt="{{ wardrobe_preview_primary_alt }}" loading="lazy" width="720" height="540"></span>
              <span class="bw-flow__choice-copy"><span class="bw-flow__choice-title">Laminate Panel</span><span class="bw-flow__choice-note">A reliable, easy-to-maintain shutter direction for most wardrobes.</span></span>
            </label>
            <label class="bw-flow__choice bw-flow__choice--image"><input type="radio" name="wardrobe_shutter_material" value="Acrylic panel">
              <span class="bw-flow__choice-media"><img src="{{ wardrobe_preview_secondary_src }}" alt="{{ wardrobe_preview_secondary_alt }}" loading="lazy" width="720" height="540"></span>
              <span class="bw-flow__choice-copy"><span class="bw-flow__choice-title">Acrylic Panel</span><span class="bw-flow__choice-note">For a more polished finish with a crisp, reflective wardrobe front.</span></span>
            </label>
            <label class="bw-flow__choice bw-flow__choice--image"><input type="radio" name="wardrobe_shutter_material" value="Mirror / glass">
              <span class="bw-flow__choice-media"><img src="{{ wardrobe_preview_quaternary_src }}" alt="{{ wardrobe_preview_quaternary_alt }}" loading="lazy" width="720" height="540"></span>
              <span class="bw-flow__choice-copy"><span class="bw-flow__choice-title">Mirror / Glass</span><span class="bw-flow__choice-note">Use when the wardrobe should enlarge the room visually and feel more premium.</span></span>
            </label>
            <label class="bw-flow__choice bw-flow__choice--image"><input type="radio" name="wardrobe_shutter_material" value="Profile / mixed finish">
              <span class="bw-flow__choice-media"><img src="{{ wardrobe_preview_tertiary_src }}" alt="{{ wardrobe_preview_tertiary_alt }}" loading="lazy" width="720" height="540"></span>
