      <div class="bw-flow__stage" data-step-panel="5">
        <div class="bw-flow__stage-head">
          <h3 class="bw-flow__stage-title">Review the wardrobe brief and send it to Bluewud</h3>
          <p class="bw-flow__stage-copy">The outcome here should be a clean consultation brief, not a superficial auto-price.</p>
        </div>
