        <div class="bw-flow__summary-line"><span>Measurements</span><strong data-summary-measurements>Enter width, height, depth</strong></div>
        <div class="bw-flow__summary-line"><span>Build</span><strong data-summary-build>Pick materials and finish</strong></div>
        <div class="bw-flow__summary-line"><span>Features</span><strong data-summary-features>Set storage features</strong></div>
        <div class="bw-flow__summary-line"><span>Mirror</span><strong data-summary-mirror>Choose mirror direction</strong></div>
      </div>
